  <chapter>
    <title>Synopsis</title>
    <para>
      OBJECTFANATICS Assertion Library is an assertion library to assert parameter values and return values by constraint annotations.
      The following values can be asserted by them.
    </para>
    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Constructor parameter
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Method parameter
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Method return value
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </chapter>

  <chapter>
    <title>Constraint Annotations</title>
    <para>
      There are some kinds of constraint annotations.
      Each annotation has its own rule and throws IllegalArgumentException (for parameter value) or IllegalStateException (for return value) when assertion is failed.
    </para>
    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term>@NotNull</term>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            throws an exception when its target value is null.
          </para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>
  </chapter>
